summary: The diff modifies ProductCatalog.tsx to populate the PRODUCTS array with 51 unique tech/gadget products spanning 10 categories (Audio, Wearables, Accessories, Smart Home, Gaming, Tablets, Cameras, Laptops, Phones, Networking). This satisfies REQ-1's requirements of at least 40 products, at least 8 categories, unique ids/names/descriptions/prices/ratings, and category filterability.
